            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股半日跌   汽車股窄幅偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日收跌，牛皮偏軟。兩市合計成交7466.23億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097537633130-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097537633130-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日收報3382點，跌2點或0.06%，今早開報3384點，平開，早段高見3391，升7點或0.21%，即迅速向下，最低見3380，跌4點或0.12%，為上午低位。半日成交2896.85億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日報10185點，跌18點或0.18%，今早開報10205點，開升2點或0.01%，早段高見10223，升20點或0.2%，近10:30am報10174點，跌29點或0.28%，為上午低位，半日成交4569.38億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日報3873點，跌4點或0.12% ; 今日開報3878，升1點或0.03%，</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日報2038，跌9點或0.48% ; 今早開報2047點，跌1點或0.05%，</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">工信部、市監總局、國家發改委據報本周在北京與比亞迪、吉利和小米等十多家主要電動汽車製造商的高管開會，要求他們「自我監督」，A股汽車股個別發展，比亞迪(002594.SZ)跌0.36%，報359.47元 ; 長安汽車(000625.SZ)跌0.92%，報12.86元 ;上汽集團(600104.SH)跌0.84%，報15.29元 ; 賽力斯(601127.SH)跌0.87%，報132.91元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14988631-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c-%e6%b1%bd%e8%bb%8a%e8%82%a1%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20190507_FI_A-SHARE_FB-1-2-3-1-5_source-ap_-2-1-1-3.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-06 11:45:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
