            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早段近平開後轉跌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3384點，平開，現跌2點或0.06%，報3381點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報10205點，開升2點或0.01%，現跌18點或0.17%，報10184。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3878，升1點或0.03%，現跌0.16點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2047點，跌1點或0.05%，現跌3點或0.17%，報2045點。</p>\n</div>",
